%%{init: {'theme':'base', 'themeVariables': {
  'primaryColor':'#dbeafe',
  'primaryTextColor':'#1e3a8a',
  'primaryBorderColor':'#1e40af',
  'lineColor':'#666666',
  'fontFamily':'Helvetica'
}}}%%
flowchart TD
    classDef action fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#1e40af,color:#1e3a8a,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef verify fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#166534,color:#14532d,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef artifact fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#92400e,color:#78350f,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef fail fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#991b1b,color:#7f1d1d,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef start fill:#e5e7eb,stroke:#4b5563,color:#1f2937,stroke-width:2px

    Start([User pushes to main / opens PR]):::start
    PreCommit{Local pre-commit hook}:::verify
    VStd[verify-standards.js<br/>V04-V10]:::verify
    VGraph[verify-id-graph.js<br/>G01-G15]:::verify

    Start --> PreCommit
    PreCommit -- commits touch .md/.js --> VStd
    PreCommit -- platform repo only --> VGraph
    VStd -- PASS --> VGraph
    VStd -- FAIL --> Block1[BLOCK: commit rejected]:::fail
    VGraph -- FAIL --> Block2[BLOCK: commit rejected]:::fail

    Push([git push]):::start
    VGraph -- PASS --> Push

    Push --> CI[GitHub Actions workflow<br/>verify-id-graph.yml]:::action
    CI --> Checkout[Checkout Z-ai-platform<br/>--recurse-submodules]:::action
    Checkout --> Std2[verify-standards.js]:::verify
    Std2 --> Graph2[verify-id-graph.js]:::verify

    Graph2 -- HARD PASS --> InstallGv[Install graphviz]:::action
    Graph2 -- HARD FAIL --> UploadFail[Upload verifier-output artifact<br/>7-day retention]:::artifact
    UploadFail --> PRComment[Comment on PR<br/>with failing checks]:::fail

    InstallGv --> GenGraph[graph-deps.sh<br/>--out=docs/_graph]:::action
    GenGraph --> GenMermaid[render-diagrams.sh<br/>--out=docs/_diagrams]:::action
    GenMermaid --> UploadGraph[Upload id-graph artifact<br/>30-day retention<br/>SVG + PNG + DOT]:::artifact
    UploadGraph --> Done([Done]):::start

    Nightly([Nightly 03:00 UTC<br/>06:00 Europe/Moscow]):::start
    Nightly --> CI
